<para style="p">

  <verse number="9" style="v" />Regarding brotherly love, you have no need for anyone to write to you, for you yourselves are taught by God to love one another.

  <verse number="10" style="v" />Indeed, you do this for all the brothers who are in all Macedonia. But we exhort you, brothers, to do this even more.

  <verse number="11" style="v" />We also exhort you to aspire to live quietly, mind your own business, and work with your hands, just as we commanded you.

  <verse number="12" style="v" />Do this so that you may walk properly in respect to those who are outside the faith, and so that you may have need of nothing.</para>
